title: Test jupyter notebook
text:
This is strictly for testing. The jupyter notebook is automatically rendered to the blog site. This means that I can render any and all jupyter notebooks to the blog site. This is a great way to share code and results.

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


x = np.linspace(0, 2 * np.pi, 100)
y = np.sin(x)

plt.plot(x, y)
